name: OxygenSaturationSaO2BldA
title: Oxygen Saturation (SaO2), BldA
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to oxygen saturation, given in decimal form, from arterial blood.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes oxygen saturation, as well as calculated method type, property of mass decimal fraction, and results in decimal fractions without units from arterial blood.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes arterial blood gas panel, and oxygen saturation levels in property (i.e., mass fraction) or method type (i.e., pulse oximetry) not listed under inclusion criteria.)
